node.text:
Happy Tuesday!
Let’s kick today off with a tour of @amberinteriors #whatsthestoryspanishglory property. When it was revealed in 2019, everything about it blew us away. The textures, the patterns, the contrast, the warmth, the arches... and its seemingly effortless ability to stay so on point with its Spanish Revival charm, yet maintain clean modern lines.
[Photos: @tessaneustadt & @amberinteriors]
